309
00:18:53.874 --> 00:18:55.391
Well. let's get it fitted.

310
00:18:55.667 --> 00:18:57.839
♪

311
00:19:01.667 --> 00:19:03.012
[steam hissing]

312
00:19:08.770 --> 00:19:12.943
- [Nico calling out]
- [cattle lowing]

313
00:19:16.632 --> 00:19:17.977
