317
00:19:28.425 --> 00:19:29.805
Send 'em.

318
00:19:29.908 --> 00:19:32.253
[cow bellows]

319
00:19:33.770 --> 00:19:35.494
[shouting]

320
00:19:35.598 --> 00:19:37.460
