Ramos!

325
00:19:47.287 --> 00:19:48.563
Is that a challenge?

326
00:19:48.632 --> 00:19:49.839
That's just a fact.

327
00:19:49.977 --> 00:19:51.632
[Zach]
Oh. it's a fact.

328
00:19:51.736 --> 00:19:53.081
You talk a big game.

329
00:19:53.150 --> 00:19:54.322
Little pretty boy talking big.

330
00:19:54.460 --> 00:19:55.908
- Pretty boy? You like that?
- Yeah.

331
00:19:55.977 --> 00:19:57.115
Your sister
said that last night.

332
00:19:57.218 --> 00:19:58.770
- [Zach] Oh.
- Hundred bucks.

333
00:19:58.839 --> 00:20:00.115
10-Petal versus Dutton.

334
00:20:00.184 --> 00:20:01.770
[Azul]
I don't want your money. I want

335
00:20:01.874 --> 00:20:03.529
- that pretty little buckle.
- Uh. you want that buckle

336
00:20:03.632 --> 00:20:05.287
- 'cause you can't win one?
- [Rip] All right. all right.

337
00:20:05.391 --> 00:20:06.943
all right. Let's settle it
