Oh. what we got here. Oz?

434
00:24:09.012 --> 00:24:10.494
- [chuckling]
- Is that a Mossberg?

435
00:24:10.632 --> 00:24:11.667
What is that?

436
00:24:11.805 --> 00:24:13.081
I like that.

437
00:24:13.150 --> 00:24:14.046
[whistles]

438
00:24:14.150 --> 00:24:16.184
♪ tense music ♪

439
00:24:16.322 --> 00:24:17.529
