[clicks tongue]

441
00:24:18.943 --> 00:24:20.667
Shit.

442
00:24:22.012 --> 00:24:23.598
Hunter or hunted. Chet.

443
00:24:23.667 --> 00:24:25.529
Hero or coward.

444
00:24:25.667 --> 00:24:28.598
You know. life always comes
down to two choices.

445
00:24:30.598 --> 00:24:31.805
Always the hunter.

446
00:24:34.081 --> 00:24:36.253
♪

447
00:24:38.908 --> 00:24:39.977
How's that one feel?

448
00:24:40.081 --> 00:24:42.287
[chuckles] Like trouble.

449
00:24:46.356 --> 00:24:47.736
How's it feel to you?

450
00:24:47.805 --> 00:24:50.253
What the fuck. man?

451
00:24:51.150 --> 00:24:52.322
Rob-Will.

452
00:24:55.115 --> 00:24:56.150
Rob-Will.

453
00:25:02.736 --> 00:25:05.218
We'll take 'em all.
[laughs]

454
00:25:05.322 --> 00:25:07.218
[both laughing]

455
00:25:07.356 --> 00:25:08.391
Smoke?

456
00:25:08.529 --> 00:25:10.081
[Oz]
Hell yeah.

457
00:25:10.218 --> 00:25:12.218
♪ upbeat country music ♪

458
00:25:12.356 --> 00:25:13.632
[Zach]
Git.

459
00:25:13.701 --> 00:25:15.839
Let's go.

460
00:25:18.839 --> 00:25:20.012
[whistling]

461
00:25:23.977 --> 00:25:26.184
- [men whooping]
- [Zach] Yes. sir.

462
00:25:26.287 --> 00:25:28.150
[grunting]

463
00:25:29.046 --> 00:25:30.770
- [cow mooing]
- [cowboy] There it is.

464
00:25:30.908 --> 00:25:32.874
