He was late. but he made it up.

465
00:25:33.805 --> 00:25:35.529
- [men cheering and whistling]
- [cowboy] Let's go.

466
00:25:35.632 --> 00:25:38.150
- [Zach] Get it. boys.
- Six-two.

467
00:25:38.943 --> 00:25:42.563
<i>♪ I was yours the day you
flashed your eyes at mine ♪</i>

468
00:25:42.667 --> 00:25:43.736
- [Guillermo] See that?
- [cowboy] Oh. yeah.

469
00:25:43.839 --> 00:25:45.184
That's how us vaqueros do it.

470
00:25:45.287 --> 00:25:46.839
- Hey. you see this?
- [Guillermo] <i>A ver.</i>

471
00:25:46.908 --> 00:25:48.218
- [Austin] See that. boys?
- [Guillermo] Mommy buy that

472
00:25:48.322 --> 00:25:49.805
