or what?

473
00:25:49.874 --> 00:25:51.184
[laughter]

474
00:25:51.287 --> 00:25:52.736
- Let's go.
- <i>♪ I put the hammer to ♪</i>

475
00:25:52.839 --> 00:25:54.701
<i>♪ The final nail this time... ♪</i>

476
00:26:03.770 --> 00:26:05.632
[bellows]

477
00:26:08.287 --> 00:26:09.218
[Guillermo]
Oh!

478
00:26:09.287 --> 00:26:10.218
Goddamn it. Frank.

479
00:26:10.322 --> 00:26:11.322
Fucker's fast.

480
00:26:11.425 --> 00:26:13.012
No. you're just fucking slow.

481
00:26:13.115 --> 00:26:14.943
Snap on that head loop
hurt your ears down here?

482
00:26:15.012 --> 00:26:17.218
[Zach] Shit. I was listening for
the stretch on that heel rope.

483
00:26:17.322 --> 00:26:19.598
I didn't hear nothing. Maybe
