487
00:26:24.081 --> 00:26:25.218
Shit. I know
how to do lots of things.

488
00:26:25.287 --> 00:26:26.598
Ask your sister. pretty boy.

489
00:26:26.701 --> 00:26:28.046
I'm head and you're heel.

490
00:26:28.150 --> 00:26:29.322
All right. Let's do it.

491
00:26:29.598 --> 00:26:31.977
♪

492
00:26:35.908 --> 00:26:37.770
No pressure.

493
00:26:43.529 --> 00:26:45.012
