494
00:26:48.494 --> 00:26:51.218
[men whooping]

495
00:26:51.322 --> 00:26:52.529
[cowboy] Golly.

496
00:26:52.632 --> 00:26:53.943
Ooh. five-five.

497
00:26:54.046 --> 00:26:56.805
