498
00:26:56.943 --> 00:26:58.425
[Zach]
So did your sister.

499
00:26:58.563 --> 00:26:59.839
[laughs]

500
00:26:59.943 --> 00:27:01.460
[indistinct chatter]

501
00:27:01.563 --> 00:27:03.356
- [Zach] Whoo. boys!
- [Austin] Damn. that was fast.

502
00:27:03.460 --> 00:27:05.494
