506
00:27:14.977 --> 00:27:18.012
No. just wanted to check
if the Angus got unloaded okay.

507
00:27:18.150 --> 00:27:19.253
They did.

508
00:27:19.356 --> 00:27:20.701
Mm.

509
00:27:20.805 --> 00:27:23.012
Can I get you
up to the house for a drink?

510
00:27:23.839 --> 00:27:25.529
Yeah. Give me an hour.

511
00:27:27.805 --> 00:27:30.012
♪ dramatic music ♪

512
00:27:35.667 --> 00:27:38.770
